<string_table>
	<string key="SWORD_FEATURE" kor="{F-2002_12}{CB-255,255,255,255}{A-L}아래의 무기를 사용할 수 있습니다.{N}플라즈마스워드, 카운터스워드, 스톰배트{N}스파이대거, 트윈 블레이드, 브레이커{N}아래의 스킬을 사용할 수 있습니다.{N}체력마스터리, 스킬마스터리" ger="{F-2002_12}{CB-255,255,255,255}{A-L}Du kannst folgende Waffen benutzen :{N}Plasma Sword, Counter Sword, Storm Bat, Spy Dagger{N}Twin Blade, Breaker{N}Du kannst folgende Skills benutzen :{N}HP Mastery, Skill Mastery" eng="{F-2002_12}{CB-255,255,255,255}{A-L}You can use the following weapons :{N}Plasma Sword, Counter Sword, Storm Bat, Spy Dagger{N}Twin Blade, Breaker{N}You can use the following skills :{N}HP Mastery, Skill Mastery" fre="{F-2002_12}{CB-255,255,255,255}{A-L}Tu peux utiliser les armes suivantes :{N}Plasma Sword, Counter Sword, Storm Bat, Spy Dagger{N}Twin Blade, Breaker{N}Tu peux utiliser les skills suivants :{N}HP Mastery, Skill Mastery" spa="{F-2002_12}{CB-255,255,255,255}{A-L}Разрешено следующее оружие:{N}Plasma Sword, Counter Sword, Storm Bat, Spy Dagger{N}Twin Blade, Breaker{N}HP+, SP+" ita="{F-2002_12}{CB-255,255,255,255}{A-L}Puoi usare le seguenti armi:{N}Plasma Sword, Counter Sword, Storm Bat, Spy Dagger{N}Twin Blade, Breaker{N}Puoi usare le seguenti skill:{N}HP Mastery, Skill Mastery." rus="{F-2002_12}{CB-255,255,255,255}{A-L}Разрешено следующее оружие:{N}Plasma Sword, Counter Sword, Storm Bat, Spy Dagger{N}Twin Blade, Breaker{N}HP+, SP+" ame="{F-2002_12}{CB-255,255,255,255}{A-L}You can use the following weapons :{N}Plasma Sword, Counter Sword, Storm Bat, Spy Dagger{N}Twin Blade, Breaker{N}You can use the following skills :{N}HP Mastery, Skill Mastery"/>
	<string key="ROOKIE_FEATURE" kor="{F-2002_12}{CB-255,255,255,255}{A-L}아래의 무기를 사용할 수 있습니다.{N}플라즈마스워드, 스톰배트, 서브머신건, 리볼버{N}세미라이플, 헤비머신건, 가우스라이플, 핸드건{N}스파이대거, 호밍라이플, 에어건, 봄버, 트윈 블레이드{N}스파크 라이플, 쇼크 웨이브 건, 브레이커{N}아래의 스킬을 사용할 수 있습니다.{N}체력마스터리, 스킬마스터리" ger="{F-2002_12}{CB-255,255,255,255}{A-L}Du kannst folgende Waffen benutzen :{N}Plasma Sword, Storm Bat, Submachine Gun{N}Revolver,Semi-Rifle, Heavy Machine Gun, Gauss-Rifle, Handgun.{N}Homing Rifle, Spy Dagger,  Air Gun, Bomber, Twin Blade{N}Spark Rifle, Shockwave Gun, Breaker{N}Du kannst folgende Skills benutzen :{N}HP Mastery, Skill Mastery." eng="{F-2002_12}{CB-255,255,255,255}{A-L}You can use the following weapons :{N}Plasma Sword, Storm Bat, Submachine Gun{N}Revolver,Semi-Rifle, Heavy Machine Gun, Gauss-Rifle, Handgun.{N}Homing Rifle, Spy Dagger, Air Gun, Bomber, Twin Blade{N}Spark Rifle, Shockwave Gun, Breaker{N}You can use the following skills :{N}HP Mastery, Skill Mastery." fre="{F-2002_12}{CB-255,255,255,255}{A-L}Tu peux utiliser les armes suivantes:{N}Plasma Sword, Storm Bat, Submachine Gun{N}Revolver,Semi-Rifle, Heavy Machine Gun, Gauss-Rifle, Handgun.{N}Homing Rifle, Air Gun,Bomber, Twin Blade{N}Spark Rifle, Shockwave Gun, Breaker{N}Tu peux utiliser les skills suivants :{N}HP Mastery, Skill Mastery." spa="{F-2002_12}{CB-255,255,255,255}{A-L}You can use the following weapons :{N}Plasma Sword, Storm Bat, Submachine Gun{N}Revolver,Semi-Rifle, Heavy Machine Gun, Gauss-Rifle, Handgun.{N}Homing Rifle, Spy Dagger,  Air Gun, Bomber, Twin Blade{N}Spark Rifle, Shockwave Gun, Breaker{N}You can use the following skills :{N}HP Mastery, Skill Mastery." ita="{F-2002_12}{CB-255,255,255,255}{A-L}Puoi usare le seguenti armi:{N}Plasma Sword, Storm Bat, Submachine Gun,{N}Revolver,Semi-Rifle, Heavy Machine Gun, Gauss-Rifle, Handgun.{N}Homing Rifle, Spy Dagger, Air Gun, Bomber, Twin Blade{N}Spark Rifle, Shockwave Gun, Breaker{N}Puoi usare le seguenti skill:{N}HP Mastery, Skill Mastery." rus="{F-2002_12}{CB-255,255,255,255}{A-L}Разрешено следующее оружие:{N}Plasma Sword, Storm Bat, Submachine Gun{N}Revolver,Semi-Rifle, Heavy Machine Gun, Gauss-Rifle, Handgun.{N}Homing Rifle, Spy Dagger, Air Gun, Bomber, Twin Blade{N}Spark Rifle, Shockwave Gun, Breaker{N}Разрешены следующие навыки:{N}HP+, SP+." ame="{F-2002_12}{CB-255,255,255,255}{A-L}You can use the following weapons :{N}Plasma Sword, Storm Bat, Submachine Gun{N}Revolver,Semi-Rifle, Heavy Machine Gun, Gauss-Rifle, Handgun.{N}Homing Rifle, Spy Dagger, Air Gun, Bomber, Twin Blade{N}Spark Rifle, Shockwave Gun, Breaker{N}You can use the following skills :{N}HP Mastery, Skill Mastery."/>
	<string key="SUPER_FEATURE" kor="{F-2002_12}{CB-255,255,255,255}{A-L}아래의 무기를 사용할 수 있습니다.{N}플라즈마스워드, 스톰배트, 서브머신건, 리볼버{N}세미라이플, 헤비머신건, 카운터스워드{N}마인드쇼크, 가우스라이플, 그레네이드건, 센티넬{N}핸드건, 스매쉬 라이플, 버스트샷건{N}스파이대거, 호밍라이플, 에어건, 봄버, 트윈 블레이드{N}스파크 라이플, 쇼크 웨이브 건, 브레이커{N}아래의 스킬을 사용할 수 있습니다.{N}체력마스터리, 스킬마스터리{N}쉴드, 블록, 인비저블, 디텍트" ger="{F-2002_12}{CB-255,255,255,255}{A-L}Du kannst folgende Waffen benutzen :{N}Plasma Sword, Storm Bat, Submachine Gun, Revolver, {N}Semi-rifle, Heavy Machine Gun, Counter Sword, {N}Mind Shock, Gauss Rifle, Senty Nell, Handgun, Smash Rifle.{N}Homing Rifle, Spy Dagger, Air Gun, Bomber, Twin Blade{N}Spark Rifle, Shockwave Gun, Breaker{N}Du kannst folgende Skills benutzen : {N}HP Mastery, Skill Mastery, {N}Shield, Block, Invisible" eng="{F-2002_12}{CB-255,255,255,255}{A-L}You can use the following weapons :{N}Plasma Sword, Storm Bat, Submachine Gun, Revolver, {N}Semi-rifle, Heavy Machine Gun, Counter Sword, {N}Mind Shock, Gauss Rifle, Senty Nell, Handgun, Smash Rifle.{N}Homing Rifle, Spy Dagger,  Air Gun, Bomber, Twin Blade{N}Spark Rifle, Shockwave Gun, Breaker{N}You can use the following skills : {N}HP Mastery, Skill Mastery, {N}Shield, Block, Invisible" fre="{F-2002_12}{CB-255,255,255,255}{A-L}Tu peux utiliser les armes suivantes :{N}Plasma Sword, Storm Bat, Submachine Gun, Revolver, {N}Semi-rifle, Heavy Machine Gun, Counter Sword, {N}Mind Shock, Gauss Rifle, Senty Nell, Handgun, Smash Rifle.{N}Homing Rifle, Spy Dagger,  Air Gun, Bomber, Twin Blade{N}Spark Rifle, Shockwave Gun, Breaker{N}Tu peux utiliser les skills suivants : {N}HP Mastery, Skill Mastery, {N}Shield, Block, Invisible" spa="{F-2002_12}{CB-255,255,255,255}{A-L}You can use the following weapons :{N}Plasma Sword, Storm Bat, Submachine Gun, Revolver, {N}Semi-rifle, Heavy Machine Gun, Counter Sword, {N}Mind Shock, Gauss Rifle, Senty Nell, Handgun, Smash Rifle.{N}Homing Rifle, Spy Dagger,  Air Gun, Bomber, Twin Blade{N}Spark Rifle, Shockwave Gun, Breaker{N}You can use the following skills : {N}HP Mastery, Skill Mastery, {N}Shield, Block, Invisible" ita="{F-2002_12}{CB-255,255,255,255}{A-L}Puoi usare le seguenti armi:{N}Plasma Sword, Storm Bat, Submachine Gun, Revolver,{N}Semi-rifle, Heavy Machine Gun, Counter Sword,{N}Mind Shock, Gauss Rifle, Senty Nell, Handgun, Smash Rifle.{N}Homing Rifle, Spy Dagger,  Air Gun, Bomber, Twin Blade{N}Spark Rifle, Shockwave Gun, Breaker{N}Puoi usare le seguenti skill:{N}HP Mastery, Skill Mastery,{N}Shield, Block, Invisible." rus="{F-2002_12}{CB-255,255,255,255}{A-L}Разрешено следующее оружие:{N}Plasma Sword, Storm Bat, Submachine Gun, Revolver, {N}Semi-rifle, Heavy Machine Gun, Counter Sword, {N}Mind Shock, Gauss Rifle, Senty Nell, Handgun, Smash Rifle.{N}Homing Rifle, Spy Dagger,  Air Gun, Bomber, Twin Blade{N}Spark Rifle, Shockwave Gun, Breaker{N}Разрешены следующие навыки:{N}HP+, SP+, {N}Shield, Block, Invisible." ame="{F-2002_12}{CB-255,255,255,255}{A-L}You can use the following weapons :{N}Plasma Sword, Storm Bat, Submachine Gun, Revolver, {N}Semi-rifle, Heavy Machine Gun, Counter Sword, {N}Mind Shock, Gauss Rifle, Senty Nell, Handgun, Smash Rifle.{N}Homing Rifle, Spy Dagger,  Air Gun, Bomber, Twin Blade{N}Spark Rifle, Shockwave Gun, Breaker{N}You can use the following skills : {N}HP Mastery, Skill Mastery, {N}Shield, Block, Invisible"/>
	<string key="S4_FEATURE" kor="{F-2002_12}{CB-255,255,255,255}{A-L}모든무기와 모든스킬을 사용할 수 있습니다." ger="{F-2002_12}{CB-255,255,255,255}{A-L}Du kannst alle Waffen und alle Skills benutzen." eng="{F-2002_12}{CB-255,255,255,255}{A-L}You can use every skill and weapon." fre="{F-2002_12}{CB-255,255,255,255}{A-L}Tu peux utiliser toutes les armes et tous les skills." spa="{F-2002_12}{CB-255,255,255,255}{A-L}Разрешены любые навыки и оружие." ita="{F-2002_12}{CB-255,255,255,255}{A-L}Puoi usare tutte le skill e le armi." rus="{F-2002_12}{CB-255,255,255,255}{A-L}Разрешены любые навыки и оружие." ame="{F-2002_12}{CB-255,255,255,255}{A-L}You can use every skill and weapon."/>
	<string key="ARCADE_FEATURE" kor="{F-2002_12}{CB-255,255,255,255}{A-L}센트리건과 센티넬을 사용할 수 없습니다.{N}플라잉, 앵커링, 블럭, 인비저블을 사용할 수 없습니다." ger="{F-2002_12}{CB-255,255,255,255}{A-L}Sentry Gun und Senty Nell können nicht verwendet werden.{N}Auch Flying, Anchoring, Block und Invisible sind nicht erlaubt." eng="{F-2002_12}{CB-255,255,255,255}{A-L}You cannot use Sentry Gun and Senty Nell.{N}You cannot use Flying, Anchoring, Block, Invisible." fre="{F-2002_12}{CB-255,255,255,255}{A-L}Tu ne peux pas utiliser les Sentry Gun et Senty Nell.{N}Tu ne peux pas utiliser Flying, Anchoring, Block, Invisible." spa="{F-2002_12}{CB-255,255,255,255}{A-L}You cannot use Sentry Gun and Senty Nell.{N}You cannot use Flying, Anchoring, Block, Invisible." ita="{F-2002_12}{CB-255,255,255,255}{A-L}Non puoi usare Sentry Gun e Senty Nell.{N}Non puoi usare Flying, Anchoring, Block e Invisible." rus="{F-2002_12}{CB-255,255,255,255}{A-L}You cannot use Sentry Gun and Senty Nell.{N}You cannot use Flying, Anchoring, Block, Invisible." ame="{F-2002_12}{CB-255,255,255,255}{A-L}You cannot use Sentry Gun and Senty Nell.{N}You cannot use Flying, Anchoring, Block, Invisible."/>
	<string key="SLAUGHTER_FEATURE" kor="{F-2002_12}{CB-255,255,255,255}{A-L}마인드 쇼크, 마인드 에너지, 블럭을 사용할 수 없습니다." ger="{F-2002_12}{CB-255,255,255,255}{A-L}Mind Shock, Mind Energy und Block sind nicht erlaubt." eng="{F-2002_12}{CB-255,255,255,255}{A-L}You cannot use Mind Shock, Mind Energy, Block." fre="{F-2002_12}{CB-255,255,255,255}{A-L}Tu ne peux pas utiliser Mind Shock, Mind Energy, Block." spa="{F-2002_12}{CB-255,255,255,255}{A-L}You cannot use Mind Shock, Mind Energy, Block." ita="{F-2002_12}{CB-255,255,255,255}{A-L}Non puoi usare Mind Shock, Mind Energy e Block." rus="{F-2002_12}{CB-255,255,255,255}{A-L}You cannot use Mind Shock, Mind Energy, Block." ame="{F-2002_12}{CB-255,255,255,255}{A-L}You cannot use Mind Shock, Mind Energy, Block."/>
